description: Design a print-ready PNG flyer for Purdue Pool with the title 'Purdue Pool' prominently displayed. Include: (1) URL 'purduepool.com', (2) Purdue Pool logo (download from 'https://purduepool.com'), and (3) use Purdue's official Black and Gold colors. Ensure the layout is clear and appealing for a general audience. The flyer should be versatile for posting or distribution anywhere.

Design a PNG flyer for Purdue Pool with the title 'Purdue Pool' prominently displayed. The flyer should include the URL 'purduepool.com' and the Purdue Pool logo, downloadable from 'https://purduepool.com'. It must use Purdue's official colors of Black and Gold. Design the flyer at letter size dimensions, ensuring a clear and appealing layout suitable for a general audience. The flyer should be versatile for posting or distribution anywhere, and be completed by next week using any common design tool that can output a PNG file. No additional images or graphics apart from the logo and text are required.
